    - target: {fileID: 4438115779432066610, guid: f56c0464f5e392c4cb451e18e85823e6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Text
      value: 'Fix the bridge!


        Press B: the bridge gradually raises and
        rotates to connect the two platforms. The amounts of raising and rotating
        may be fed as script input (try it out once it works to figure out the ideal
        values).


        When the bridge works, make sure that our worker can actually
        ride it and move between the platforms.


        Once you''re done, fly
        to the next planet!'
